:name:
Magister

:coretxt:
Control over large masses. This typically cannot be resisted. It can only be noticed.

:cost:
1 Reason

:req:
You have gathered large, violent mob.

:1:
Induce general feeling to audience.

:2:
Summon an audience you want. 
If someone is unable or extremely unwilling to participate they can send someone else on their behalf.
However, if they cannot find anybody, they will do everything in their power to be there as soon as possible.

:3:
Appear as the absolute authority.

:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricMindControl
